Package: escrocR
Title: EscrocR: a R package implementing the models ESCROC and EscroPath
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Hilaire","Drouineau",email="hilaire.drouineau@irstea.fr",role=c("aut","cre")),
    person("Marine","Ballutaud",role=c("aut")),
    person("Jeremy","Lobry",email="jeremy.lobry@irstea.fr",role=c("aut")))
Description: Escroc is a model that aims at estimating contaminant biomagnification, isotopic enrichments and diet in trophic networks, Escropath is a Bayesian coupling of Escroc and Ecopath.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
